column5: It must be. But it wasn't caught anywhere in North America. That's a European pike.
ya i belive it was in an esox angler magizene this year, the article was on pike fishing in europe.
Apparently my friend was telling me about the 55 lb pike he seen a pic of that was caught in Manitoba.
I caught that pike last year on a trip to Rice Lake...
What's my fish doing in that guy's hands?
